## Africana Studies Relation

**Africana Studies Relation:**  
The NAACP is a cornerstone of African-American activism and advocacy. Its efforts in law, politics, and cultural preservation provide essential insights into the Black freedom struggle and are widely studied in Africana Studies programs.

